data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
You can either create a new instance, or convert an existing instance to the correct mod pack.
Note: If you convert an existing instance, all mods and mod config files will be overwritten by the new pack.

data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
When you click the button, depending on what you selected above, either a new instance will be created or an existing instance will be converted to the correct modpack for the server.
This cannot be undone!
